60@unknown@formal@none@1@S@From The Law of Outdoor Activities@1@6@@oe@20-11-2007
80@unknown@formal@none@1@S@§1: Definitions of cultivated and non-cultivated area.@1@7@@oe@20-11-2007
110@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Small areas without production that are next to cultivated areas, or fenced in with such are also regarded as cultivated areas.@1@21@@oe@20-11-2007
