140@unknown@formal@none@1@S@As non-cultivated area is in this law meant areas without production which is not regarded as cultivated area.@1@18@@oe@20-11-2007
160@unknown@formal@none@1@S@§2: Entry of non-cultivated area@1@5@@oe@20-11-2007
