220@unknown@formal@none@1@S@§3: Entry of cultivated area@1@5@@oe@20-11-2007
240@unknown@formal@none@1@S@In cultivated areas, anyone can enter on foot in the time of the year when the ground is frozen or covered with snow, but not in the time from 30. of April to 14. of October.@1@36@@oe@20-11-2007
250@unknown@formal@none@1@S@This right is not for yard or built area, fenced garden or park or other specially-purpose fences area where the entry of people at winter-time undoubtly would be troublesome for owner or user.@1@33@@oe@20-11-2007
270@unknown@formal@none@1@S@§9 Camping@1@2@@oe@20-11-2007
