4740@unknown@formal@none@1@S@There is also a train-line from Östersund (Sweden) to Trondheim.@1@10@@oe@20-11-2007
4750@unknown@formal@none@1@S@This is served by several trains each day with connections to Stockholm.@1@12@@oe@20-11-2007
