5020@unknown@formal@none@1@S@By Car@1@2@@oe@20-11-2007
5040@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Taking your own car to Norway can be a very nice experience.@1@12@@oe@20-11-2007
5050@unknown@formal@none@1@S@Be aware of the special driving conditions in the country, especially in the winter.@1@14@@oe@20-11-2007
